			<testcase
			id="b79c4b6d-a882-4fe3-a518-380ef26e6669"
			name="PLM_Mechanical_Deploy_Test"
			reportlevel="Info;20">
				<description>
					<![CDATA[<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>Activate task pane after close drawing</P>
<P>Wait for save in before checkin with drawing</P>
<P>Delay before delete files</P>
<P>Reload req when checking for complete</P>
<P>Release current item is slow on second run because absolute path works but 
cached path does not</P>
<P>Task pane logout fails in approveRWOSolidWorks and ApproveReqSolidWorks</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>Environment variable can be one of:</P>
<P><IMG id=Img636270738510914495 
src="file:///C:/Users/kdekroon/AppData/Local/Temp/bcda93ea-0ef1-44e9-8671-cbd2f0e33e4c/1"></P>]]>
				</description>
				<parameters>
					<param
					name="RunEnvironment"
					value="QA Cambridge">
					</param>
					<param
					name="MacroPath"
					value="&quot;\\ca01a9001\pgmis\Development\ATSPLM PLM Test Files\Cust property change Revisions2.xls&quot;">
					</param>
					<param
					name="SolidWorksPath"
					value="C:\SldWorks2016\SOLIDWORKS\SLDWORKS.exe">
					</param>
					<param
